Author: Duskyroses
Text: 1,400 doesn’t sound like “too much” hun. 💕 congrats on taking a big leap forward! I think you will be able to stick with recovery!   I’m going to check out Kate Noel right now ☺️ I’m also in the midst of recovery and I’m glad you’re doing the right things for you too! Recovery has genuinely made me happier :) I hope it does for you too.
